Package org.bonitasoft.engine.bpm.data

Interface DataDefinition

All Superinterfaces:
BonitaObject, DescriptionElement, NamedElement, Serializable, Visitable
All Known Subinterfaces:
TextDataDefinition, XMLDataDefinition
All Known Implementing Classes:
DataDefinitionImpl, TextDataDefinitionImpl, XMLDataDefinitionImpl
public interface DataDefinition extends DescriptionElement, Visitable
It forms part of the ProcessDefinition. It is used to define a date in the context of a ProcessDefinition or a FlowNodeDefinition.
Since:
6.0.0
Author:
Matthieu Chaffotte, Feng Hui, Celine Souchet
